      "text": "Pronunciation?"
    },
    {
      "start": 107.14,
      "end": 107.32,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 107.6,
      "end": 111.18,
      "text": "What about their pronunciation is special or surprising?"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.32,
      "end": 112.48,
      "text": "다 그런 건 아니지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.48,
      "end": 115.56,
      "text": "특히 루실하고 루실의 엔트 있잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 115.92,
      "end": 117.24,
      "text": "그 이몬지 고몬지."
    },
    {
      "start": 117.38,
      "end": 117.62,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 118.02,
      "end": 118.64,
      "text": "That 분."
    },
    {
      "start": 118.9,
      "end": 119.38,
      "text": "그분."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.58,
      "end": 121.66,
      "text": "그분들의 발음 한번 생각을 해보세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 121.92,
      "end": 122.42,
      "text": "기억나세요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 122.54,
      "end": 123.5,
      "text": "기억이 잘 나는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.5,
      "end": 125.3,
      "text": "프랑스 어경영이였네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 125.4,
      "end": 125.68,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 125.86,
      "end": 127.28,
      "text": "French accent."
    },
    {
      "start": 127.28,
      "end": 127.64,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 128.28,
      "end": 130.78,
      "text": "그 액센트 굉장히 attractive하지 않았습니까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 130.8,
      "end": 131.76,
      "text": "How was it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.76,
      "end": 132.68,
      "text": "It was kind of airy."
    },
    {
      "start": 132.82,
      "end": 133.08,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 133.36,
      "end": 134.86,
      "text": "약간 그 공기 반 소리 반."
    },
    {
      "start": 134.94,
      "end": 136.2,
      "text": "약간 그렇기도 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.2,
      "end": 138.92,
      "text": "뭔가 좀 파리 여성 같은 느낌이 물씬 났어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 139.02,
      "end": 139.86,
      "text": "아 파리 여성."
    },
    {
      "start": 139.94,
      "end": 141.34,
      "text": "A French woman."
    },
    {
      "start": 141.58,
      "end": 141.74,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 141.84,
      "end": 142.72,
      "text": "Elegant French woman."
    },
    {
      "start": 142.84,
      "end": 143.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.14,
      "end": 144.64,
      "text": "파리 여성이라고 하니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.64,
      "end": 146.56,
      "text": "갑자기 그 드라마도 생각이 납니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 147.12,
      "end": 147.72,
      "text": "Emily in Paris."
    },
    {
      "start": 147.74,
      "end": 148.12,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 148.32,
      "end": 148.9,
      "text": "Did you see that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.94,
      "end": 149.14,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 149.22,
      "end": 149.66,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 149.72,
      "end": 150.78,
      "text": "시즌 2도 봤어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 150.92,
      "end": 151.46,
      "text": "I did too."
    },
    {
      "start": 151.52,
      "end": 152.28,
      "text": "I saw both seasons."
    },
    {
      "start": 152.46,
      "end": 155.14,
      "text": "But honestly, I liked season 1."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.2,
      "end": 155.62,
      "text": "저도요."
    },
    {
      "start": 155.62,
      "end": 156.34,
      "text": "Much more."
    },
    {
      "start": 156.48,
      "end": 156.66,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 156.8,
      "end": 157.16,
      "text": "저도요."
    },
    {
      "start": 157.18,
      "end": 158.86,
      "text": "But it was a very entertaining show."
    },
    {
      "start": 158.92,
      "end": 159.2,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 159.2,
      "end": 161.76,
      "text": "But I heard French people do not like that show."
    },
    {
      "start": 162.12,
      "end": 163.0,
      "text": "Some French people."
    },
    {
      "start": 163.12,
      "end": 163.4,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 163.56,
      "end": 171.5,
      "text": "They either hate it or they think it's ridiculous because it's a view, it's an American view of French life and French people."
    },
    {
      "start": 171.5,
      "end": 181.42,
      "text": "American view라고 하셨으니까 말인데 이 영화에서 프랑스 여성들, 프랑스 사람들에 대한 이야기가 막 나오잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 181.42,
      "end": 185.06,
      "text": "Were they similar to the image that you had?"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.14,
      "end": 187.28,
      "text": "The image I had of French people?"
    },
    {
      "start": 187.4,
      "end": 187.72,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 187.72,
      "end": 188.7,
      "text": "I think so."
    },
    {
      "start": 188.84,
      "end": 190.0,
      "text": "Especially with Lucille."
    },
    {
      "start": 190.22,
      "end": 190.36,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 190.56,
      "end": 197.76,
      "text": "Lucille's very, I think of French women as very strong and like independent and strong-spirited."
    },
    {
      "start": 197.76,
      "end": 201.62,
      "text": "And they don't just go with society or go with the flow."
    },
    {
      "start": 201.74,
      "end": 202.22,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 202.3,
      "end": 202.96,
      "text": "And Lucille."
    },
    {
      "start": 203.14,
      "end": 203.3,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 203.44,
      "end": 206.96,
      "text": "I mean, this rich guy, powerful guy, like proposed to her."
    },
    {
      "start": 207.02,
      "end": 207.24,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 207.28,
      "end": 208.14,
      "text": "She turned him down."
    },
    {
      "start": 208.18,
      "end": 208.44,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 208.54,
      "end": 210.16,
      "text": "And she seems like a very strong lady."
    },
    {
      "start": 210.34,
      "end": 210.52,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 210.68,
      "end": 212.36,
      "text": "And she has good fashion sense."
    },
    {
      "start": 212.4,
      "end": 212.6,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 212.7,
      "end": 215.1,
      "text": "She has like a hat and she's always wearing fancy dresses."
    },
    {
      "start": 215.34,
      "end": 215.62,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 215.62,
      "end": 224.32,
      "text": "And she seems like, yeah, she seems of what the kind of character that I thought of as a regular just French, elegant French lady."
    },
    {
      "start": 224.48,
      "end": 225.38,
      "text": "와, 그렇군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 225.4,
      "end": 229.7,
      "text": "이거는 나만의 그 좁은 미국인이시가지만 그냥 내 생각이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 230.1,
      "end": 243.02,
      "text": "저도 비슷한 약간의 prejudice라고 할 수도 있겠는데 좀 좋은 쪽으로 프랑스인에 대한 편견을 가지고 있었는데 그것을 잘 반영을 하지 않았나라고 개인적으로 생각을 했습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 243.02,
      "end": 246.56,
      "text": "그나저나 이 Lucille을 연기한 배우 아시죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.8,
      "end": 248.14,
      "text": "Vanessa Paradis."
    },
    {
      "start": 248.3,
      "end": 248.86,
      "text": "Paradis."
    },
    {
      "start": 248.96,
      "end": 249.18,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.6,
      "end": 252.4,
      "text": "이 사람도 is also actually French잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 252.78,
      "end": 253.02,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 253.4,
      "end": 257.76,
      "text": "그러면 이 사람이 이 Lucille에 대해서 가장 잘 이해하고 있겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 258.22,
      "end": 258.58,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 258.74,
      "end": 261.6,
      "text": "And she actually really identified with Lucille."
    },
    {
      "start": 261.72,
      "end": 262.68,
      "text": "She said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.68,
      "end": 273.38,
      "text": "Lucille is someone who tries to do the right thing without upsetting anyone while also remaining her own woman, which can be a very difficult thing to do."
    },
    {
      "start": 273.58,
      "end": 280.6,
      "text": "She tries to not get anybody angry, but also be her own woman and do her own way or go her own way."
    },
    {
      "start": 281.06,
      "end": 284.3,
      "text": "So she's both constrained and independent."
    },
    {
      "start": 284.3,
      "end": 302.04,
      "text": "And she also runs a cabaret, which involves a lot of responsibility and pressure, and she has a really bossy aunt who likes to be obeyed and wants Lucille just to be a goody two-shoes, a perfect little niece, but she doesn't really want to listen to her aunt."
    },
    {
      "start": 302.04,
      "end": 308.7,
      "text": "So I think she does, yeah, it is a French spirit is embodied by Lucille."
    },
    {
      "start": 309.06,
      "end": 313.06,
      "text": "네. 우리가 예상했던 그대로가 다 반영이 되어 있는 캐릭터인 것 같고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 313.64,
      "end": 317.96,
      "text": "들으면 들을수록 she has a strong ego를 가지고 있는 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 318.14,
      "end": 318.8,
      "text": "Strong ego."
    },
    {
      "start": 318.92,
      "end": 320.06,
      "text": "Not too big."
    },
    {
      "start": 320.78,
      "end": 328.68,
      "text": "남한테 피해주진 않으면서 자기 자신의 자존심 아니면 자긍심이 굉장히 높은 케이스라고 정리할 수 있겠네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 328.96,
      "end": 330.78,
      "text": "네. 좋게 좋게 정리합시다."
    },
    {
      "start": 330.78,
      "end": 335.0,
      "text": "Big ego는 안 좋은 거고, Strong ego는 좋은 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 335.12,
      "end": 335.86,
      "text": "네. 좋습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 335.88,
      "end": 336.58,
      "text": "She's a strong woman."
    },
    {
      "start": 336.96,
      "end": 338.44,
      "text": "오늘 장면 듣고 오겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 339.2,
      "end": 341.04,
      "text": "Ow! You're hurting me!"
    },
    {
      "start": 341.08,
      "end": 343.78,
      "text": "Not as much as you've hurt me."
    },
    {
      "start": 344.32,
      "end": 347.12,
      "text": "Your words carry no weight until longer, my dear."
    },
    {
      "start": 347.54,
      "end": 353.16,
      "text": "Now let's stop with this little charade and at least have one moment of true honesty between us."
    },
    {
      "start": 353.5,
      "end": 354.5,
      "text": "Where is it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 354.56,
      "end": 355.48,
      "text": "Where is what?"
    },
    {
      "start": 355.66,
      "end": 357.28,
      "text": "Uh, sir, it's in there."
    },
    {
      "start": 357.64,
      "end": 360.14,
      "text": "First you accuse me without a shred of evidence."
    },
    {
      "start": 360.14,
      "end": 362.72,
      "text": "Then you violate my private property."
    },
    {
      "start": 363.56,
      "end": 367.36,
      "text": "If you dare to enter my dressing room, you will have to find another singer."
    },
    {
      "start": 367.36,
      "end": 371.17,
      "text": "어제 장면 기억나시겠죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 371.61,
      "end": 375.71,
      "text": "Albert got told some information to Maynard, the commissioner."
    },
    {
      "start": 376.27,
      "end": 378.15,
      "text": "Uh-oh, he's a tattletale."
    },
    {
      "start": 378.27,
      "end": 380.89,
      "text": "He told on his own co-worker."
    },
    {
      "start": 381.11,
      "end": 381.85,
      "text": "그러니까요."
    },
    {
      "start": 382.01,
      "end": 388.15,
      "text": "그래서 이 서장이요, 이 루실의 분장실에 와서 수색을 하고 있는 장면이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 388.15,
      "end": 390.67,
      "text": "He is tearing up her dressing room."
    },
    {
      "start": 390.67,
      "end": 396.55,
      "text": "They're throwing, opening the dressers, throwing the clothes all over, looking for the flea monster."
    },
    {
      "start": 397.25,
      "end": 404.67,
      "text": "지난번에 루실한테 달콤하게 고백할 땐 언제고, 지금은 뭐, he's completely changed his attitude."
    },
    {
      "start": 404.67,
      "end": 408.17,
      "text": "그러니까 지금 거의 눈이 뵈는 게 없는 상태."
    },
    {
      "start": 408.49,
      "end": 408.97,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 409.09,
      "end": 410.55,
      "text": "아주 180%."
    },
    {
      "start": 410.55,
      "end": 413.03,
      "text": "응, 제가 하고 싶은 말 그대로 해주셨어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 413.39,
      "end": 417.01,
      "text": "He just lost any respect I had for him."
